data.description: 2020 build Tanzanite two story home you’ve been waiting for! Spacious living in this 4 bed 3 bath home with some added updates. Walking in you will fall in love with huge window overlooking the luxuriously finished garage. Super sweet! Very functional kitchen with lots of cabinet and counter (quartz counter top) top space, walk in pantry, open to the living and dining areas. Off the dining space open the sliding doors to the backyard that features a gorgeous updated porch, an awesome relaxing in ground POOL, and a privacy fenced backyard. Second floor you have all 4 beds, full bath plus master bathroom. Basement is finished and has been turned into a theatre room. Such a cool place to see with some high end add ons. Call your favorite Realtor and come take a look today!
